originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.id AS aka_id,
    a.name AS aka_name,
    t.id AS title_id,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    t.production_year,
    p.info AS person_info,
    c.kind AS cast_kind
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id
JOIN 
    role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000 AND 
    c.kind = 'actor'
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    a.name ASC

    t.production_year,
    p.info AS person_info,
    c.kind AS cast_kind
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id
JOIN 
    role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000 AND 
    c.kind = 'actor'
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    a.name ASC
